
On behalf of Jeff Skilling, I'm writing to encourage you to join the Harvard 
Business School Club of Houston.  Benefits of the club are:

Interesting speaker and panel programs
Stimulate discussion of current business/social problems
Promote business/social relationships among area alumni
Bring HBS news to area alumni
Communicate area alumni views to the alumni office
Assist/facilitate MBA student/local employer contacts
Provide community service
Cooperate with the Alumni office to strengthen the local club and encourage 
the establishment of new clubs.
